01:04:00.840 --> 01:04:02.950
Any way that we
could, without some

01:04:02.950 --> 01:04:05.470
sort of evil that
we have to fight,

01:04:05.470 --> 01:04:08.050
is there any way
that we can increase

01:04:08.050 --> 01:04:11.320
the speed of, I don't
know, research progress

01:04:11.320 --> 01:04:16.060
or at least the
development side of R&D,

01:04:16.060 --> 01:04:18.280
if we can make it that quick?

01:04:18.280 --> 01:04:22.690
